# SprintCRM

SprintCRM is an internal outbound CRM for managing imported lead databases, daily work queues, warm contacts, pipeline stages, reports, and safe data cleanup.

It was built as a personal-use operational CRM, not as a public SaaS or email automation tool. The main goal is to support a disciplined manual outbound workflow: import leads, clean and deduplicate data, work through the daily queue, manage active contacts, monitor the pipeline, and export reports.

## Project Type

- Internal tool
- Product prototype
- Operational CRM system
- Personal outbound workflow system

## Core Workflow

```text
Import CSV/XLSX
→ map columns
→ preview and deduplicate
→ create leads
→ work through Today queue
→ manage each lead in the Work Panel
→ monitor warm contacts and pipeline
→ review reports
→ export or clean data safely
@'
